OL,3,C'It's like a miracle': Six-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl has eyesight restored by gene
OL,5,Ctherapy
OL,7,FSaffie was five years old when she was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with a rare condition that
OL,9,Fmeant she had no vision in low light
OL,10,Fand could end up losing her vision
OL,11,Fcompletely if not treated, as ITV News
OL,12,FHealth Correspondent Rebecca Barry
OL,13,Freports
OL,15,FThe parents of a six-year-old girl
OL,16,Fwhose eyesight has been restored by
OL,17,Fgene therapy have described the
OL,18,Fresults as a "miracle".
OL,26,@zD@NOUzD@VO]
