OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776906184
OL,3,C'It's like a miracle': Six-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl has eyesight restored by gene
OL,5,Ctherapy
OL,7,FSaffie Sandford, from Stevenage in
OL,8,FHertfordshire, has a rare genetic
OL,9,Fcondition called Leber's Congenital
OL,10,FAmaurosis, which causes blindness.
OL,12,FChildren with the condition typically
OL,13,Fhave very little vision in daylight,
OL,14,Fand none in low light. It can lead to
OL,15,Fcomplete loss of sight by adulthood.
OL,17,FBy the age of five, Saffie needed to
OL,18,Fuse a torch to eat her meals and was
OL,19,Funsteady on her feet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
