PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776906184
OL,3,C'It's like a miracle': Six-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl has eyesight restored by gene
OL,5,Ctherapy
OL,7,FSaffie's mum, Lisa Sandford, spoke to
OL,8,FITV News about the day they received
OL,9,Fthe diagnosis.
OL,11,F"We both just cried," said Lisa. "You
OL,12,Fcan't comprehend losing your eyesight
OL,13,F- and you definitely can't comprehend
OL,14,Fit for your child."
OL,16,FBut in 2025, Saffie had life-changing
OL,17,Fgene therapy at Great Ormond Street
OL,18,FHospital (GOSH).
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@UO]sD@bOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
