PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776906184
OL,3,C'It's like a miracle': Six-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl has eyesight restored by gene
OL,5,Ctherapy
OL,7,FSaffie has a faulty RPE 65 gene, which
OL,8,Fprevents cells in the eye making a
OL,9,Fprotein needed for vision.
OL,11,FA modified virus was injected directly
OL,12,Finto the back of Saffie's eyes,
OL,13,Fintroducing healthy copies of the gene
OL,14,Finto the cells.
OL,16,FSaffie can now, for the first time,
OL,17,Fsee her parents' faces in the dark;
OL,18,Fshe has learnt to ride a bike, enjoys
OL,19,Ftrampolining and swimming ` all
OL,20,Factivities that she struggled to do
OL,21,Fbefore the treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
