PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776906184
OL,3,C'It's like a miracle': Six-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl has eyesight restored by gene
OL,5,Ctherapy
OL,7,FTraditional eye tests can be difficult
OL,8,Ffor young children, so the research
OL,9,Fteam measured the electrical impulses
OL,10,Fbeing sent from the retina to the
OL,11,Fbrain. Seventy per cent of the
OL,12,Fchildren showed improvements after
OL,13,Ftreatment.
OL,15,FThe team hopes this evidence will lead
OL,16,Fto more investment in gene therapy for
OL,17,Fchildren with other forms of rare
OL,18,Fgenetic blindness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
